    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> 30 August 2024</p>

    <p>Thank you for using <strong>PaoPao Money Manager</strong> ("the App"). Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy
        Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our App.</p>

    <h2>1. What information does the Application obtain and how is it used?</h2>
    <p>The Application may collect certain information automatically, including, but not limited to, the type of mobile device you use, 
	your mobile operating system. All the information above is needed to the app's function for you. </p>

    <h2>2. Does the Application collect your personal information of the device?</h2>
    <p>This Application does not collect any personal information of your mobile device. 
	The Application do not have account system, so we will not ask you for personal information (such as your name, email address and an account password). 
	We don’t collect your Unique Device ID (‘UDID’) and/or IP address and/or GPS location.
	All the app’s personal information will be saved on your phone or your own third services, 
	such as Google Drive or Dropbox and iCloud, so no information of yours will be uploaded.</p>

    <h2>3. Children</h2>
    <p>We do not use the Application to knowingly solicit data from or market to children under the age of 13. 
	If a parent or guardian becomes aware that his or her child has provided us with information without their consent, 
	he or she should contact us via email glgjingmarvel@gmail.com. We will delete such information from our files within a reasonable time.</p>

    <h2>4.Changes</h2>
    <p>This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time for any reason. 
	You are advised to consult this Privacy Policy regularly for any changes, as continued use is deemed approval of all changes.</p>

    <h2>5. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or for other operational,
        legal, or regulatory reasons. We will notify you of any significant changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on
        this page. Please review this Privacy Policy periodically to stay informed about how we protect your
        information.</p>

    <h2>6. Contact Us</h2>
